Articles.Content:
Question:

does a ram air intake, increase the power/efficiency at altitude of the kethane mod's zero bypass turbine?

the two intake resources look different

ram intake=IntakeAir

zero bypass= KintakeAir.
looks like it doesnt work with the keth turb.

You could probably make a custom config that uses a stock intake to bring in KintakeAir instead. Not reeeeealy sure what the point would be except maybe as an eve ssto.

Or better yet simply copy and paste the KintakeAir lines from the engine and paste them into the stock ram intake .cfg. Have that intake do both jobs simultaneously so you don't add new parts to your part list.

Edited June 5, 2013 by HoY
